class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-how-to-open-a-bar-checklist-420x320-20200928.jpeg?crop=21:16,smart&width=210&dpr=2" width="210" height="160" alt="">
</picture></div></div></div><div
class="col-md-8"><h2>How to Open a Bar — Checklist</h2><p>Download our free checklist in PDF format to help you stay on track when opening your bar.</p><a
href="https://www.zarla.com/downloads/zarla-how-to-open-a-bar-checklist-20230926.pdf" class="btn btn-primary btn-download" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" download>Download Now</a></div></div></div></div><div
class="block block-how-to"><h2 id=how-to-open-a-bar>How to Open a Bar:</h2><div
class="how-to-info"><div
class="info">
