 top of the search results, making yourself attractive to potential customers. <\/p>\n<p>Search engine marketing (SEM) helps you rank in Google search results, making you visible to more potential customers.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-open-a-bar#how-to-open-a-bar-section10-step4","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-register-with-google-288x288-20200818.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"},"itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToTip","text":"<p>SEM is a highly technical field, so you may benefit from using a marketing agency if you're short on the skill set.<\/p>\n"}]}]}]}</script> <div
